text: Kathleen Wilton was a New Zealand rugby union player. She played for the New Zealand women's national rugby union team at the 2014 Women's Rugby World Cup. She studied at University of Otago. She played for Alhambra Union Rugby Football Club and Eketahuna (WB). == References == == Other websites == * Black Ferns Training Session, 23 July 2014 Category:Living people Category:New Zealand rugby union players Category:1984 births
